OLYMPIA PROPERTIES, L.L.C., Plaintiff-Appellant, v. UNITED STATES, Defendant-Appellee. No. 03-5039. United States Court of Appeals, Federal Circuit. July 17, 2003.

Before NEWMAN, MICHEL, and RADER, Circuit Judges.

JUDGMENT

PER CURIAM.
